      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh wow okay i didn't realize it was that serious. i thought because it was just a plant it wouldn't really mess with the meds that much. are you sure though? i've read some things online saying that as long as you don't take huge doses it's fine. like maybe if i just take a small amount it wouldnt really trigger anything like that? it just seems like a lot to go to the doctor just for a supplement.",
